k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9ecqok.png&h=e2acf12f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你可以留意下HKMC官方指引：<br />\nwebsite:<a href=\"http://www.hkmc.com.hk/files/press_release/330/chi/Press%20Release_Amendments%20to%20the%20Mortgage%20Insurance%20Programme_Chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmc.com.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpress_release%2F330%2Fchi%2FPress%2520Release_Amendments%2520to%2520the%2520Mortgage%2520Insurance%2520Programme_Chi.pdf&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoLis81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=246f55c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkmc.com.hk/files/press_release/330/chi/Press%20Release_Amendments%20to%20the%20Mortgage%20Insurance%20Programme_Chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論是新的按揭政策還是舊的按揭政策，HKMC做8成一向<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有</span></span></span></strong>要求必須首置。<br />\n<br />\n舉例： 你有一個已經供滿的物業。現時你買入另一個物業自住，只要你提供到證明是自住，按指引，HKMC最多是可以批出8成按揭。<br />\n<br />\n過去，也有人是持有多於一個按揭。例如，本身沒有物業，只是替近親擔保按揭，現時到自己買入自住物業，就可以做最多9成。不過就要給多一點保費。這個保費表HKMC也是有的。<br />\n<br />\n不過，如果你現時的單位是你的名下，並有按揭。那就要視乎你買入的新物業的價格和是否自住（or放租）。按指引最多是做4-5成按揭。"}]}